   4059				     ; Input: CfgData.BaudRate (DWORD)
   4060				     ; Output: BX = divisor value
   4061				     ; Destroys: AX, CX, SI
   4062	39DD			     LookupBaudDivisor PROC
   4063	39DD  57			 push	 di
   4064	39DE  BE 26ADr			 lea	 si, BaudTable
   4065
